# LucidGate example list: oldexceptionphraselist
# Format: One plain phrase per line. Matching is streaming and case-insensitive in the semantic/masking filters.
# Lines beginning with # are comments and are ignored by the loader.
# To activate a rule, copy one example, remove the leading # and adapt it to your environment.
# You can include another file with: .Include<relative-or-absolute-path>
#
# Commented examples:
# credential dump
# private api key
# internal admin password
# malware staging url
# phishing landing page
# exploit kit marker
# password reset token
# confidential roadmap
# secret signing key
# production database dump
